    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Effective Date: April 29, 2025</p>

    <h2>What Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use our contact form, we collect your name, email address, subject, and message. This information is used solely to respond to your enquiry.</p>

    <h2>Why We Collect Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your enquiries</li>
      <li>To provide customer support</li>
      <li>To improve our services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How Your Data Is Stored</h2>
    <p>Your enquiry is sent directly to our secure email inbox at <strong>office@mcquote.co.uk</strong> and is not stored on our web server. We retain the information only as long as needed to support your request.</p>


    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data at any time. To exercise these rights, email us at <strong>office@mcquote.co.uk</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Third Parties</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal information with any third parties. We do not use your data for marketing without your explicit consent.</p>

    <h2>Data We Automatically Collect</h2>
    <p>When you interact with our website (e.g., upload a job or submit a form), we may collect certain technical data including your IP address, browser type, and device information. This data is used for security, fraud prevention, and service optimization. Your IP address may also be used to help match you with nearby bodyshops.</p>

    <h2>Use of Google reCAPTCHA</h2>
    <p>We use Google reCAPTCHA v2 to protect our forms against bots and abuse. This service may collect information about your device, browser, and IP address as part of the verification process. It is subject to Google's <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Terms of Service</a>.</p>

    <h2>Payments with Stripe</h2>
    <p>When you make a payment on our website, your transaction is securely processed by Stripe. We do not store your payment card details. Stripe may collect personal data such as your IP address, email, and transaction metadata. Please review <a href="https://stripe.com/gb/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stripe's Privacy Policy</a> for more information.</p>

    <h2>Location Services via OpenCage API</h2>
    <p>We use the OpenCage Geocoding API to convert postcode information into geographic coordinates. This helps us allocate jobs to nearby bodyshops. Your location data is used only for this purpose and is not stored permanently. For details, refer to the <a href="https://opencagedata.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OpenCage Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>Customer Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We only keep customer information for as long as necessary to provide our service and support your request. Once your job is completed, rejected, or no longer active, your personal data and images are securely deleted from our systems.</p>
    
    <p>We do not retain customer data for marketing or profiling purposes. You may request the deletion of your data at any time by contacting us at <strong>office@mcquote.co.uk</strong>.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this policy or your data, please contact us at <strong>office@mcquote.co.uk</strong>.</p>
  

